---
layout: base.njk
title: HVAC Blog | Tips & Insights from Santa Valley HVAC
description: HVAC maintenance tips, energy-saving advice, and air quality insights from Santa Valley's trusted heating and cooling experts
---

<section class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
        <h1>HVAC Tips & Insights</h1>
        <p>Expert advice on heating, cooling, and air quality from our certified technicians</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="blog-listing">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="blog-grid">
            {% for post in collections.blog %}
            <article class="blog-card">
                <h2><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h2>
                <div class="post-meta">
                    <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}">{{ post.date | postDate }}</time>
                    {% if post.data.author %}
                    <span class="author">by {{ post.data.author }}</span>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
                <p>{{ post.data.excerpt }}</p>
                <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="read-more">Read More</a>
            </article>
            {% endfor %}
        </div>
    </div>
</section>